      "title": "NO paddy for animal feed: CAA",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Consumer Affairs Authority has issued an extraordinary gazette prohibiting any importer,\u00a0 manufacturer, trader or distributor shall import, sell, expose or offer for\u00a0sale, store, transport, distribute or buy or purchase any rice or paddy directly for the manufacture of animal feed or otherwise\u00a0as an ingredient for the manufacture of animal feed.",
